      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Variability across multiple pump specimens and fluid batches must be characterised to establish experimental repeatability bounds for the validation dataset.",
      "rationale": "Inter-specimen variability assessment across multiple manufactured pump units was not performed; only a single FDA benchmark unit was used in the PIV validation experiments. Characterisation of unit-to-unit geometric variation and its effect on hemolysis was considered outside the scope of the present credibility assessment."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
