    "rationale": "Ten of thirteen credibility factors have been assessed and all meet or exceed their required gradation levels for MRL 3. The three unassessed factors (Model inputs, Test samples, Equivalency of input parameters) were considered beyond the scope of the current analysis phase. The assessment team concluded that the assessed evidence is sufficient to support the intended use decision, and that the unassessed factors do not materially affect the overall credibility conclusion given the conservative margins observed in assessed factors.",
